  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RE-EXIT</strong> is an anomaly horror game that challenges your perception and attention to detail. Trapped in a temporal loop caused by an unexplained anomaly, your mission is to observe your surroundings carefully, survive, and report any irregularities to find a way out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay Overview:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Anomaly Detection:</strong> Each time you loop, scrutinize the corridor for any changes. Anomalies can be <strong>subtle</strong> or <strong>overt</strong>, testing your observational skills.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/5a75e6621715341e08c0a22a319cfc81.poster.avif?t=1764446994\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/5a75e6621715341e08c0a22a319cfc81.webm?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/5a75e6621715341e08c0a22a319cfc81.mp4?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Puzzles:</strong> Solve puzzles that test your logic and observation skills</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/a1266e00d0b81cb854e46d4051682255.poster.avif?t=1764446994\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/a1266e00d0b81cb854e46d4051682255.webm?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/a1266e00d0b81cb854e46d4051682255.mp4?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Threats and Traps:</strong> Encounter deadly enemies and  traps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/6a69a28ccfb907c6d6fb24f2ef5637b6.poster.avif?t=1764446994\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/6a69a28ccfb907c6d6fb24f2ef5637b6.webm?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/6a69a28ccfb907c6d6fb24f2ef5637b6.mp4?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Break the Loop:</strong> Successfully identify anomalies eight times in a row to  realign the distortions and escape the loop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/6d65a18071d384cb336c2855a3c45620.avif?t=1764446994\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras_big/6d65a18071d384cb336c2855a3c45620.avif?t=1764446994 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Estimated Playtime: </strong>Approximately 3-4 hours, to discover and experience all anomalies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can you trust your senses enough to escape the loop?</strong><br><br><br><br><strong></strong><br><br><br><br><strong>Developer's Note:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>RE-EXIT</i> is developed by a solo indie developer. Your support and feedback are highly appreciated and will help in refining the game further.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RE-EXIT</strong> is an anomaly horror game that challenges your perception and attention to detail. Trapped in a temporal loop caused by an unexplained anomaly, your mission is to observe your surroundings carefully, survive, and report any irregularities to find a way out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay Overview:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Anomaly Detection:</strong> Each time you loop, scrutinize the corridor for any changes. Anomalies can be <strong>subtle</strong> or <strong>overt</strong>, testing your observational skills.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/5a75e6621715341e08c0a22a319cfc81.poster.avif?t=1764446994\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/5a75e6621715341e08c0a22a319cfc81.webm?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/5a75e6621715341e08c0a22a319cfc81.mp4?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Puzzles:</strong> Solve puzzles that test your logic and observation skills</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/a1266e00d0b81cb854e46d4051682255.poster.avif?t=1764446994\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/a1266e00d0b81cb854e46d4051682255.webm?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/a1266e00d0b81cb854e46d4051682255.mp4?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Threats and Traps:</strong> Encounter deadly enemies and  traps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/6a69a28ccfb907c6d6fb24f2ef5637b6.poster.avif?t=1764446994\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/6a69a28ccfb907c6d6fb24f2ef5637b6.webm?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/6a69a28ccfb907c6d6fb24f2ef5637b6.mp4?t=1764446994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Break the Loop:</strong> Successfully identify anomalies eight times in a row to  realign the distortions and escape the loop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/6d65a18071d384cb336c2855a3c45620.avif?t=1764446994\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras_big/6d65a18071d384cb336c2855a3c45620.avif?t=1764446994 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Estimated Playtime: </strong>Approximately 3-4 hours, to discover and experience all anomalies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can you trust your senses enough to escape the loop?</strong><br><br><br><br><strong></strong><br><br><br><br><strong>Developer's Note:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>RE-EXIT</i> is developed by a solo indie developer. Your support and feedback are highly appreciated and will help in refining the game further.</p>",
